title: Wall Street Breakfast April 19:  Housing Market Hits an Inflection Point (Podcast)
author: Seeking Alpha

description: Investors will get more data on the U.S. housing market today. Signs are emerging that Q1 earnings season will be more disappointing than expected. Recent statistics released by both New Jersey and Pennsylvania point to strong growth in sportsbook activity.
